{"tid":286171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擺低隻蕉同隻狗喺車度6個鐘 官怒屌狗主：你覺得隻狗識得自己剝蕉食？","createTime":"2017-06-16T11:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T11:45:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e66ccfd4e6893516ea158ebe97d2bf5cb4ff567d","tid":286171,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"狗主去年因寓所租約期滿，新居又不准養狗，遂與其松鼠狗暫時蝸居私家車上。去年12月9日狗主將車泊於露天停車場，將車窗稍為打開及放下一隻未剝皮香蕉後往上班，途人發現狗兒被獨留於車上報警。狗主今認罪，辯方今求情指事發日因趕上班，匆忙下沒留下食水，裁判官問「隻蕉冇剝皮，佢諗住隻狗識剝？」律師答「被告係諗住隻狗識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170615/large/1497498416_9f50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170615%2Flarge%2F1497498416_9f50.jpg&h=d8f5b5e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">涉案松鼠狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170615/56830746\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170615%2F56830746&d=k99%2BLdsjN01hEffRXBsamHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=752520d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170615%2F56830746&h=d06a8160\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170615/56830746</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170615/large/1497498415_5984.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170615%2Flarge%2F1497498415_5984.jpg&h=523f7f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">被告何鴻基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (蔡少玲攝)(蘋果日報)</span></div><br />\n<br />\n被告何鴻基（51歲）今承認殘酷對待動物罪，指他於去年12月9日在西貢西沙路水浪窩露天停車場私家車內，掌管被禁閉或被關禁的一隻狗，但疏於對該動物提供充足清水。<br />\n<br />\n控方申請將涉松鼠狗交由愛協照顧，但辯方求情指被告視涉案松鼠狗如兒子看待，每月花三分一人工養狗，為有多點時間照顧愛犬，被告已轉職薄餅速遞。惟裁判官稱「佢唔駛諗！佢冇權養狗！！搞到隻狗咁！」更謂若有可能，會下令被告以後不准養狗。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，被告原與母親及松鼠狗居於大嶼山，他們因業主收樓而遷往東涌，但基於公屋不准養狗，被告曾將狗寄居於寵物澡堂，後因太掛念愛犬才愚蠢地領回牠一同暫居車內。辯方又指被告每日上班也會放下水、香蕉及調低車窗，事發日因趕上班匆忙下沒留下水。裁判官問「隻蕉冇剝皮，佢諗住隻狗識剝？」律師答「被告係諗住隻狗識食」。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官將案押至7月28日判刑，並稱不排除判監，期間被告獲准保釋，並領取其社會服務令報告。"},{"pid":"75053c0dfa696c579d2aaf173b5f4d9b366f5c0c","tid":286171,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"案情指當日早上8時許<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有人於西貢水浪窩露天停車場發現一頭松鼠狗被獨留車中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，車內有一隻香蕉但無食水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，車窗打開約2厘米 。途人以為狗主往行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，惟至下午1時許途人仍見松鼠狗於車內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，於是通知愛協到場。當時陽光猛烈，車內悶熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，松鼠狗表現呆滯疲倦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。警方接報到場召來被告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，警誡下被告保持緘默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"c7aacd23f75dd5c7da961003df23ff4887f9bf06","tid":286171,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"455e06552b964a1b6583b36e03400eb5ba157009","tid":286171,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"自己識咬開架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91342f65331f232cce600b4d6f462e53daf0726","tid":286171,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"六個鐘都唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}